Hi guys! Please remember if you are watching the solar eclipse today:

PLEASE. WEAR. ECLIPSE. GLASSES. 

The eclipse will begin approximately at 1:55pm but will not reach its peak until 3:12pm. It will end at approximately 4:27pm. 

Also attached is a great way to recycle your eclipse glasses after if you do not plan on keeping them as a keepsake. 

Our very delayed March program will be a grab and go program TONIGHT at 7:30pm. 

A ‚Äúgrow your own herb‚Äù kit with an info sheet on environmental wellness, and a QR code to scan for your very own compost bin will be in the Neil LOBBY for you guys to grab :) 

It will be first come first serve so please stop by and grab one as soon as you can.

Happy Monday and happy eclipse day! Keep those eyes protected!!! Only 3 more weeks left, I am so proud of you guys, KEEP GOING!!!! ‚ù§Ô∏è ‚ù§Ô∏è ‚ù§Ô∏è
